des: This Amazon Alexa Drizzle Skill Set mission is to determine if it will rain in the next hour or not in Washington DC.This skill can be used before going for a walk,shopping,office etc to get weather update for an hour in washington
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
